  "texts": [
    "Given the constraints of our dataset size, the researchers opted for transfer learning and trained our model on the MobileNet V2 CNN architecture.",
    "This choice was motivated by MobileNet V2's excellent fit for realtime applications and its ability to handle any input image more significant than 32 x 32 pixels.",
    "The researchers used an input image shape of 128 x 128 pixels in this study.",
    "Video segments were standardized for feature extraction, with 20 frames uniformly selected and resized from each video to match the input requirements of our chosen architecture.",
    "Following feature extraction, the next stage is classification, which uses LSTM."
  ],
